VolleyStats for Android

An app for tracking player stats during a volleyball game.

The skills tracked are:
- Passing: 1, 2, 3, 4 (1 best, 4 worst)
- Serving: 1, 2, 3, 4 (1 best, 4 worst)
- Attack: Won, Nulled, Lost
- Blocks won
- Service aces

Attacks won, blocks won and service aces are summarized to calculate scored points for player.

Average of passing and serving for players are calculated.

Attacking effect for players are calculated.